Package org.netlogo.extension.r

Class Summary
Entry Class to provide access to Gnu R from NetLogo.
Entry.ClearWorkspace Class to clear R workspace.
Entry.Eval Class to evaluate submitted String in R without results.
Entry.Get Class to evaluate submitted String in R, and send back the results to NetLogo.
Entry.interactiveShell Class to setup InteractiveShell.
Entry.LoadHistory Class to load R history from file.
Entry.messageWindow Class to open MessageWindow.
Entry.Put Class to create a new R-Variable/Array from NetLogo-Values.
Entry.PutAgent Class to create a new Vector from Agent-Variables.
Entry.PutAgentDataFrame Class to create a new R-DataFrame from Agent-Variables.
Entry.PutDataframe Class to create a new R-DataFrame from NetLogo-Values.
Entry.PutNamedVector Class to create a new named R-Vector from NetLogo-Values.
Entry.PutVector Class to create a new R-Vector from NetLogo-Values.
Entry.SaveHistory Class to save R history into file.
Entry.startDebug Class to set Debug of R extension.
Entry.startJRIDebug Class to set Debug of JRI.
Entry.stopDebug Class to stop Debug of R extension.
Entry.stopJRIDebug Class to stop Debug of JRI.
HoldRengineX Class to store the R connection and to transform data.
